          <h1>The Place</h1>
          <p>
            Ekdara, Jhajha is a village in the Jamui district of Bihar, known
            for its calm surroundings and simple lifestyle. Situated close to
            Jhajha town, the area is well connected by road and rail, making it
            accessible for students from nearby villages and towns. The locality
            is peaceful and away from the rush of city life, giving children an
            ideal atmosphere for focused learning. <br /><br />
            With its greenery, open spaces, and safe environment, Ekdara
            provides a healthy setting for education and character building. It
            is in this serene place that St. Columbus Public School stands as a
            center of learning, discipline, and values. The school is a blessing
            for the local community, offering children the opportunity to
            receive quality education close to home, while growing in a
            nurturing and supportive environment.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="the-place-second-part">
          <img src="/images/school-environment.webp" alt="school-environment" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- HISTORY -->
      <section class="history container">
        <div class="history-first-part">
          <img src="/images/school-environment.webp" alt="school-environment" />
        </div>
        <div class="history-second-part">
          <h1>History</h1>
          <p>
            St. Columbus Public School, Ekdara, Jhajha (Jamui, Bihar) was
            established in 2002 to provide quality education to children of
            Ekdara and nearby villages. At that time, proper schools were
            limited in the region, and the institution was founded to make
            learning accessible and supportive for rural families. The school
            began with just a few classrooms and a small number of students,
            gradually earning the trust of parents through its focus on
            academics, discipline, and values. <br /><br />
            Over the years, the school has introduced important facilities such
            as a library to encourage reading and a playground for games and
            physical activities. Today, St. Columbus Public School stands as a
            respected educational institution, providing a safe and nurturing
            environment where students can grow academically, socially, and
            morally, preparing them to become responsible and confident
            individuals.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

