              limited in the area, the school started with only a few classrooms
              and a small group of students. Through dedication, discipline, and
              a commitment to strong values, it gradually grew into a trusted
              institution supported by both parents and the local community.
              <br />
              Over the years, the school has expanded its facilities to include
              a library that inspires reading and knowledge, as well as a
              playground where children build fitness, teamwork, and confidence.
              Today, St. Columbus Public School continues to provide a safe,
              nurturing, and disciplined environment where students are
              encouraged to excel in academics while also developing character
              and life skills that prepare them for a bright future.
            </p>
            <div class="founder-names">
