            >
            <p>
              At St. Columbus Public School, we believe in nurturing young minds
              with care and dedication. From an early age, students are
              encouraged to develop respect for values, discipline, and
              diversity, which prepares them for life in a changing world. The
              school provides an environment where every child is seen as
              unique, with qualities that must be recognized and developed.
              <br />
              Our committed team of teachers works with dedication to provide
              the best possible opportunities for learning and growth. With a
              well-structured curriculum, a supportive library, and a playground
              for physical development, we ensure that students receive balanced
              exposure to academics, co-curricular activities, and moral values.
              The aim of St. Columbus Public School is to build confident,
              responsible, and well-rounded individuals ready to face the future
              with strength and character.
            </p>
            <div class="founder-names">
              <b><%= admins[1].position%></b>
              <p><%= admins[1].name%></p>
              <p>St. Columbus Public School</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
